        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Marketers have a long history of breaking their toys.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "As soon as a tactic is proven to work and becomes commonplace, it’s often easily abused, causing the gatekeepers (i.e. Google) to ignore the tactic or penalize it.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Exact match ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "anchor text",
          "marks": [
            "link-0"
          ]
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": ", for example, ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "used",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " to be a ranking factor. Now it’s not. And the reason it’s not is because marketers tried to game the system.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [
        {
          "_key": "link-0",
          "_type": "link",
          "href": "https://youtu.be/HMycqZRxcOw?t=280"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "This reminds me of ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "something else I read",
          "marks": [
            "link-0"
          ]
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " that highlights an important point: a tactic that ‘works’ is one that can be easily gamed.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [
        {
          "_key": "link-0",
          "_type": "link",
          "href": "https://seths.blog/2021/09/messing-with-stratherns-law/"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "And a tactic that can be easily gamed is one that will easily spread. And, as such, soon chastened or abolished.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Which is why it’s best to lean on strategy, ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "not tactics",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": ". Because, over a long enough time frame, only ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "one",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " of them will get you somewhere you actually want to be.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "…",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Halo fans will remember the infamous ",
